<section class="section" id="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-title">
  <h2 id="problem-title">The Problem</h2>
  <p>Filament-only pricing misses the actual print cost. Real-world quoting includes multiple cost drivers:</p>
  <div class="section-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Filament Alone Is Incomplete</h3>
      <p>Many makers only price by grams used, which underestimates your final cost.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Electricity Is Printer-Specific</h3>
      <p>Power draw varies by machine and print length, and should be part of every quote.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Failed Prints Are Real Loss</h3>
      <p>A realistic failure risk percentage changes your expected cost outcome.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Labour and Overhead Matter</h3>
      <p>Prep, post-processing, and running costs are often ignored but directly impact margin.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="solution" aria-labelledby="solution-title">
  <h2 id="solution-title">The Solution</h2>
  <p>The app calculates true end-to-end print cost with a detailed, understandable breakdown.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Filament cost calculation with multi-material support</li>
    <li>Electricity cost integration per printer profile</li>
    <li>Failure risk modelling</li>
    <li>Labour and processing time input</li>
    <li>Detailed line-item cost breakdown</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="section" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-title">
  <h2 id="features-title">Key Features</h2>
  <div class="section-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Multi-Material Support</h3>
      <p>Split prints across multiple filaments with weight-based costing.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>G-code Import (Beta)</h3>
      <p>Import supported G-code metadata to pre-fill print weight, duration, and preview data where available.</p>
      <p class="card-note">Availability depends on slicer and export settings. G-code import is in beta; send feedback directly from the app.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Print History</h3>
      <p>Save jobs, search history, review full cost breakdowns, and export CSVs.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Material Tracking</h3>
      <p>Track remaining filament stock and automatically deduct usage when saving prints.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Printer Profiles</h3>
      <p>Store power usage and settings for multiple printers.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Detailed Cost Breakdown</h3>
      <p>Understand electricity, filament, risk, labour, and totals at a glance.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>CSV Export</h3>
      <p>Export jobs for bookkeeping, reporting, or analysis.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Offline by Default</h3>
      <p>Use the app fully offline with no accounts, logins, or cloud dependency for all features.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

